doc.after: St Michael s Golden Domed Monastery Ukrainian translit Mykhaylivs kyi zolotoverkhyi monastyr is a functioning monastery in Kiev Ukraine The monastery is located on the Western side of the Dnieper River on the edge of a bluff northeast of the St Sophia Cathedral The site is located in the historic and administrative Uppertown and overlooks the city s historical commercial and merchant quarter the Podil neighbourhood
